Danshun,

00:03:31.010 --> 00:03:32.170
I'm not sure if you know

00:03:32.170 --> 00:03:33.500
my bond with Kaifu.

00:03:34.940 --> 00:03:35.890
No matter how far

00:03:36.570 --> 00:03:37.660
Qin Hong runs,

00:03:37.890 --> 00:03:39.010
