=Episode 5=

00:05:10.220 --> 00:05:16.700
(2013/12/17, Tuesday)

00:05:17.850 --> 00:05:19.610
This video was from the surveillance

00:05:19.610 --> 00:05:21.730
of the Gaoqi Transit Station
in the Pingtan suburbs.

00:05:22.610 --> 00:05:25.410
Lyu Danshun and Qin Hong
jumped off the truck here

00:05:26.900 --> 00:05:28.610
and then moved into a blind spot.

00:05:31.120 --> 00:05:32.410
According to our investigation,

00:05:32.410 --> 00:05:34.780
the truck came from Chang'an Town.

00:05:34.980 --> 00:05:36.280
So, they most likely slipped out

00:05:36.280 --> 00:05:37.730
through the mountain roads

00:05:37.730 --> 00:05:39.850
after we locked down the town.

00:05:40.410 --> 00:05:42.050
Lyu Danshun said

00:05:42.660 --> 00:05:44.410
he used to work in Pingtan.

00:05:45.100 --> 00:05:47.170
Qin Hong was once in Pingtan, too.

00:05:47.850 --> 00:05:49.540
We now suspect those two

00:05:49.540 --> 00:05:50.890
have contacted each other earlier.

00:05:52.410 --> 00:05:54.730
Then why did they go back to Pingtan?

00:05:54.980 --> 00:05:56.410
That's still unclear for now.

00:05:56.850 --> 00:05:58.490
But we've sent people

00:05:58.490 --> 00:05:59.900
to track them down in Pingtan.

00:06:00.290 --> 00:06:01.780
Who's that kid in the video?

00:06:01.780 --> 00:06:02.700
(2013/12/17, Tuesday)

00:06:03.410 --> 00:06:04.610
Her name is Chen Yiting.

00:06:04.610 --> 00:06:05.440
We did some digging.

00:06:05.440 --> 00:06:06.490
Her parents are divorced.

00:06:06.490 --> 00:06:07.850
Her mother's name is Zhang Yan.

00:06:07.850 --> 00:06:09.100
Her father is Chen Tonghe.

00:06:10.220 --> 00:06:12.540
Lyu Danshun claimed Zhang Yan
was his girlfriend.

00:06:12.540 --> 00:06:14.980
I went back to Chencang
to meet Qin Hong's mother.

00:06:15.340 --> 00:06:16.980
At her elderly home,

00:06:16.980 --> 00:06:18.390
I found a transferred sum of money.

00:06:18.730 --> 00:06:21.100
The sender's name on it was Zhang Yan.

00:06:21.540 --> 00:06:22.660
It seems

00:06:22.660 --> 00:06:25.100
Qin Hong wired the money

00:06:25.100 --> 00:06:27.220
under Zhang Yan's name.

00:06:27.660 --> 00:06:28.710
As for Zhang Yan herself,

00:06:28.710 --> 00:06:30.590
we haven't been able to reach her.

00:06:30.660 --> 00:06:33.410
But her household registration is
in Shimen under Pingtan.

00:06:33.410 --> 00:06:34.930
Chief Liu and I will head there soon.

00:06:36.610 --> 00:06:38.660
There are too many loose ends
in Ma Weicheng's case.

00:06:39.660 --> 00:06:41.730
Qin Hong isn't even dead,

00:06:42.220 --> 00:06:43.780
and now we have Lyu Danshun

00:06:44.100 --> 00:06:45.410
and Zhang Yan.

00:06:47.100 --> 00:06:49.730
We need to figure out the connections

00:06:50.540 --> 00:06:51.680
between these people first.

00:06:53.610 --> 00:06:55.000
After Qin Hong committed the murder

00:06:55.000 --> 00:06:56.220
and disappeared from Chencang,

00:06:56.220 --> 00:06:57.410
we looked into Lyu Danshun.

00:06:57.850 --> 00:06:59.390
There was no sign of suspicion on him.

00:07:00.050 --> 00:07:01.380
We also didn't find any evidence

00:07:01.380 --> 00:07:03.250
of his contact with Qin Hong.

00:07:03.340 --> 00:07:05.290
Later, the tattoo store where he worked

00:07:05.290 --> 00:07:06.220
was demolished,

00:07:06.220 --> 00:07:07.540
so he went south to find work.

00:07:08.100 --> 00:07:10.220
So, Lyu Danshun has been lying.

00:07:10.540 --> 00:07:12.290
He actually stayed in contact
with Qin Hong

00:07:12.290 --> 00:07:13.290
and even helped her out.

00:07:13.780 --> 00:07:15.980
I suspected he was lying that day.

00:07:17.900 --> 00:07:18.750
Later, we found out

00:07:18.750 --> 00:07:20.540
that on the night
Huang Shuquan was killed,

00:07:20.540 --> 00:07:22.980
he carried a suitcase
with 600,000 in cash.

00:07:23.610 --> 00:07:24.660
But at the crime scene,

00:07:24.660 --> 00:07:26.150
that suitcase was nowhere to be found.

00:07:28.100 --> 00:07:29.080
Back then, we suspected

00:07:29.080 --> 00:07:31.390
that Qin Hong had left with the money.

00:07:31.660 --> 00:07:32.780
But later, we reconsidered.

00:07:32.980 --> 00:07:35.340
It'd be strange for Qin Hong

00:07:35.780 --> 00:07:36.980
to carry that much cash around.

00:07:37.660 --> 00:07:39.100
What about Lyu Danshun?

00:07:40.980 --> 00:07:42.540
Maybe he brought the money to Pingtan

00:07:42.540 --> 00:07:44.540
and met up with Qin Hong here.

00:07:45.900 --> 00:07:47.780
It's not some decent job.

00:07:48.290 --> 00:07:49.290
But the pay was good.

00:07:52.540 --> 00:07:53.410
Earlier, we suspected

00:07:53.410 --> 00:07:55.730
that Qin Hong used
Zhang Yan's identity to transfer money.

00:07:56.730 --> 00:07:58.660
But Zhang Yan's child, Chen Yiting,

00:07:58.660 --> 00:08:00.410
was with Qin Hong and Lyu Danshun.

00:08:03.660 --> 00:08:05.900
That proves Zhang Yan
had ties with them.

00:08:07.100 --> 00:08:08.660
It wasn't just about a stolen identity.

00:08:11.660 --> 00:08:13.490
But where is Zhang Yan now?

00:08:13.700 --> 00:08:18.060
(Hongben Inn)

00:08:58.890 --> 00:09:00.700
Mengmeng's probably been exhausted.

00:09:01.340 --> 00:09:02.340
She fell asleep.

00:09:05.220 --> 00:09:06.730
How do we get in touch with them?

00:09:13.140 --> 00:09:15.340
(Feichuan)

00:09:19.100 --> 00:09:20.220
It's too risky. Let me go.

00:09:23.610 --> 00:09:25.100
This thing started because of me.

00:09:26.250 --> 00:09:27.090
I'll go.

00:09:41.370 --> 00:09:42.220
Hello.

00:09:42.340 --> 00:09:44.220
Do you know where Zhang Yan lives?

00:09:45.460 --> 00:09:46.490
Go straight ahead.

00:09:46.490 --> 00:09:47.330
Straight ahead?

00:09:47.620 --> 00:09:48.490
Thanks.

00:09:48.610 --> 00:09:49.450
Thank you.

00:10:17.490 --> 00:10:18.330
Ma'am.

00:10:20.100 --> 00:10:20.940
Ma'am?

00:10:24.100 --> 00:10:25.340
Who are you looking for?

00:10:27.340 --> 00:10:28.180
Hello.

00:10:28.490 --> 00:10:29.330
Hello.

00:10:29.490 --> 00:10:31.820
Is this Zhang Yan's home?

00:10:34.220 --> 00:10:35.060
Why are you

00:10:35.340 --> 00:10:36.700
looking for her?

00:10:38.730 --> 00:10:39.570
Police.

00:10:40.250 --> 00:10:41.820
We need to ask a few questions.

00:10:42.940 --> 00:10:44.490
I don't know where she is.

00:10:44.850 --> 00:10:46.100
Has something happened to her?

00:10:49.490 --> 00:10:50.730
Who are you to her?

00:10:51.850 --> 00:10:52.690
I...

00:10:53.730 --> 00:10:54.850
I'm her mother.

00:10:57.120 --> 00:10:57.980
Here's the thing.

00:10:57.980 --> 00:11:00.100
She's connected to one of our cases.

00:11:00.100 --> 00:11:01.610
But we haven't been able to reach her.

00:11:01.610 --> 00:11:03.460
Could you help us try to find her?

00:11:04.980 --> 00:11:05.820
I...

00:11:12.250 --> 00:11:13.220
Don't worry.

00:11:13.220 --> 00:11:15.100
I just need to ask a few questions.

00:11:16.770 --> 00:11:18.320
Do you two talk often?

00:11:58.250 --> 00:11:59.090
What are you doing?

00:12:00.220 --> 00:12:01.100
Who let you in?

00:12:01.730 --> 00:12:02.820
Get out.

00:12:02.820 --> 00:12:03.680
Hello.

00:12:03.730 --> 00:12:04.570
I'm a police officer.

00:12:04.940 --> 00:12:07.100
I need to ask Zhang Yan a few questions.

00:12:09.230 --> 00:12:10.200
There's no such person.

00:12:10.220 --> 00:12:11.490
Leave.

00:12:11.730 --> 00:12:12.610
Go.

00:12:12.730 --> 00:12:13.570
Leave.

00:12:14.100 --> 00:12:14.940
Go.

00:12:16.580 --> 00:12:17.730
What are you doing?

00:12:17.730 --> 00:12:19.890
You didn't even notice someone
walked into our house.

00:12:20.100 --> 00:12:21.980
You're not cooking
but busy chatting instead.

00:12:22.250 --> 00:12:23.370
Trying to starve me or what?

00:12:24.700 --> 00:12:26.340
Help my mom inside.

00:12:27.060 --> 00:12:28.700
Mom, here.

00:12:28.700 --> 00:12:29.610
So clueless.

00:12:34.250 --> 00:12:35.580
Do you know where Zhang Yan is?

00:12:36.140 --> 00:12:37.610
As I told you, there's no such person.

00:12:37.610 --> 00:12:38.450
Leave.

00:12:48.340 --> 00:12:50.010
What a strange family.

00:12:51.610 --> 00:12:53.100
How did your questioning go?

00:12:53.850 --> 00:12:55.100
That was her mother.

00:12:55.100 --> 00:12:56.340
She kept stammering,

00:12:56.340 --> 00:12:58.380
as if she knew something
but didn't dare to say it.

00:12:59.490 --> 00:13:01.130
Look how her husband treats her.

00:13:01.730 --> 00:13:02.850
She's scared of him.

00:13:15.500 --> 00:13:17.020
(Generous Buddha Blessings)

00:13:23.370 --> 00:13:24.650
May the Buddha bless us.

00:13:25.250 --> 00:13:26.250
May the Buddha bless us.

00:13:32.940 --> 00:13:33.950
May the Buddha bless us.

00:13:44.130 --> 00:13:46.490
Are you still in touch with Zhang Yan?

00:13:48.100 --> 00:13:49.370
About two months ago,

00:13:49.980 --> 00:13:51.850
she sent me a text message.

00:13:55.660 --> 00:13:58.820
(Daughter: Mom, I took Mengmeng abroad.
I'll contact you once we settle down.)

00:13:58.850 --> 00:14:00.700
Do you know exactly where they went?

00:14:00.980 --> 00:14:01.820
No idea.

00:14:03.130 --> 00:14:05.490
We hardly talk.

00:14:05.980 --> 00:14:07.460
Did something happen to her?

00:14:09.730 --> 00:14:11.460
Why is it that you and your husband

00:14:11.730 --> 00:14:13.220
both don't want to mention Zhang Yan?

00:14:15.340 --> 00:14:16.220
Her dad

00:14:16.220 --> 00:14:17.580
thinks Zhang Yan brings bad luck,

00:14:17.780 --> 00:14:19.220
so he doesn't want to talk about her.

00:14:19.220 --> 00:14:20.490
What do you mean by that?

00:14:21.730 --> 00:14:24.130
My husband's family has some old taboos.

00:14:24.610 --> 00:14:26.940
Only men are allowed on the boat.

00:14:27.820 --> 00:14:30.370
They think a daughter doesn't mean much.

00:14:30.980 --> 00:14:32.340
When Zhang Yan was born,

00:14:32.340 --> 00:14:33.980
her dad didn't like her from the start.

00:14:34.700 --> 00:14:35.540
Later on,

00:14:35.730 --> 00:14:37.180
I gave birth to her younger brother,

00:14:37.820 --> 00:14:39.730
and she was pretty much forgotten.

00:14:41.340 --> 00:14:42.480
Whenever her dad was upset,

00:14:42.610 --> 00:14:45.250
he would take it out on her.

00:14:46.820 --> 00:14:48.490
When she turned 14,

00:14:48.940 --> 00:14:50.460
she fought back once.

00:14:50.940 --> 00:14:53.460
She ended up
with bruises around her eye.

00:14:54.220 --> 00:14:55.220
I told her:

00:14:55.490 --> 00:14:56.850
I went through the same thing.

00:14:58.730 --> 00:14:59.820
If you don't fight back,

00:15:00.220 --> 00:15:01.850
you'll get hurt less.

00:15:02.340 --> 00:15:04.340
That's what it means to be a woman.

00:15:07.730 --> 00:15:09.490
What kind of logic is that?

00:15:10.130 --> 00:15:11.610
You're outsiders,

00:15:11.610 --> 00:15:12.490
so you don't get it.

00:15:13.580 --> 00:15:14.490
Before Zhang Yan

00:15:15.220 --> 00:15:16.730
finished high school,

00:15:16.730 --> 00:15:18.220
her dad arranged a betrothal.

00:15:18.980 --> 00:15:21.250
She married Chen Tonghe
from the neighboring village.

00:15:22.220 --> 00:15:23.340
They barely saw each other

00:15:23.580 --> 00:15:25.610
before getting married.

00:15:26.490 --> 00:15:28.610
But at the wedding,

00:15:28.610 --> 00:15:30.610
I remember Zhang Yan
seemed pretty happy.

00:15:31.490 --> 00:15:32.330
Maybe she just wanted

00:15:32.730 --> 00:15:34.580
to get away from home asap.

00:15:34.850 --> 00:15:36.100
Is Chen Yiting

00:15:36.610 --> 00:15:37.490
their daughter?

00:15:38.370 --> 00:15:39.210
Yeah.

00:15:39.940 --> 00:15:41.580
Her nickname is Mengmeng.

00:15:42.610 --> 00:15:44.340
Where's her husband now?

00:15:46.820 --> 00:15:48.580
He died while out fishing at sea.

00:15:51.580 --> 00:15:53.130
They never even found his body.

00:15:53.980 --> 00:15:56.730
Zhang Yan's in-laws decided
she was no longer of any use,

00:15:56.730 --> 00:15:58.980
so they kicked her and the kid out.

00:15:59.610 --> 00:16:00.730
She took the kid

00:16:00.730 --> 00:16:01.850
and went to work in the city.

00:16:01.850 --> 00:16:02.820
So, the last time

00:16:03.100 --> 00:16:04.940
you were in touch was

00:16:05.580 --> 00:16:06.730
two months ago?

00:16:07.940 --> 00:16:08.780
Yeah.

00:16:09.610 --> 00:16:11.850
She even transferred 50,000 to me.

00:16:12.220 --> 00:16:14.730
I only noticed it later
when I checked the accounts.

00:16:16.200 --> 00:16:17.070
Chief Chen.

00:16:24.100 --> 00:16:25.700
Have you ever met these two?

00:16:28.700 --> 00:16:29.610
No.

00:16:31.130 --> 00:16:32.340
Officer,

00:16:32.580 --> 00:16:34.100
did something happen?

00:16:35.100 --> 00:16:37.370
What's that case you mentioned about?

00:16:37.370 --> 00:16:38.220
We haven't figured

00:16:38.220 --> 00:16:39.340
everything out yet.

00:16:40.340 --> 00:16:41.850
But if Zhang Yan reaches out to you,

00:16:42.490 --> 00:16:43.610
you must let us know.

00:16:44.490 --> 00:16:45.850
We're trying to help her,

00:16:45.980 --> 00:16:46.850
not hurt her.

00:16:47.100 --> 00:16:47.940
Chief Liu.

00:16:48.460 --> 00:16:49.300
We've got a new lead.

00:16:51.490 --> 00:16:52.330
That's it.

00:17:01.130 --> 00:17:02.080
- Hello.
- Hi.

00:17:02.820 --> 00:17:03.730
She reached out to us.

00:17:04.010 --> 00:17:05.860
Zhang Yan used to rent her apartment.

00:17:06.140 --> 00:17:07.420
If this were earlier in the year,

00:17:07.490 --> 00:17:08.430
I could've rented it out

00:17:08.430 --> 00:17:09.830
within two weeks.

00:17:10.010 --> 00:17:11.490
But now it's the end of the year.

00:17:11.710 --> 00:17:13.630
Most people have gone back
to their hometowns.

00:17:13.700 --> 00:17:15.730
Yet they insisted on moving out now.

00:17:15.860 --> 00:17:17.140
Are you saying

00:17:17.330 --> 00:17:18.700
someone else was living here

00:17:18.980 --> 00:17:20.460
besides Zhang Yan?

00:17:20.620 --> 00:17:22.330
Yeah, Zhang Yan was here
with her daughter

00:17:22.330 --> 00:17:23.330
and a man.

00:17:27.220 --> 00:17:28.090
Was it this man?

00:17:31.490 --> 00:17:32.540
Yeah, that's him.

00:17:32.660 --> 00:17:34.010
He was Zhang Yan's boyfriend.

00:17:35.010 --> 00:17:36.180
Do you know Zhang Yan?

00:17:37.180 --> 00:17:38.220
She's my girlfriend.

00:17:57.490 --> 00:17:58.940
Have you cleaned up this place?

00:17:59.220 --> 00:18:00.180
No, I haven't.

00:18:00.380 --> 00:18:01.770
At first, I was really upset.

00:18:02.220 --> 00:18:03.490
They have a kid with them.

00:18:03.490 --> 00:18:04.380
I thought

00:18:04.710 --> 00:18:05.700
that when they moved out,

00:18:05.700 --> 00:18:07.380
the place would be left in a total mess.

00:18:07.460 --> 00:18:09.290
But it turned out spotless.

00:18:09.290 --> 00:18:10.700
Not a single item was left behind.

00:18:10.730 --> 00:18:12.570
When did they say they were leaving?

